Weather
•	Takes out 1-3 workstations for 3-9 shifts
•	Options:
o	Move subjobs on those machines to other machines if possible
	Pushing the subjobs on those machines out
o	Wait it out for those subjobs	
Workstation breakdown
•	Takes out a machine for 3-9 shifts
•	Options:
o	Move subjobs on those machines to other machines if possible
o	Wait it out for those subjobs
Materials not here
•	Halts subjob until they arrive
•	Options:
o	Wait for materials for a couple shifts
o	Use another subjobs
	Delays another subjob a couple shifts (which may be fine if its not waiting)
ECHO recommendation (rare)
•	Do you want to use the recommendation of this thing to speed you up?
•	Options:
o	Take advice
	All subjobs lose a shift or two of work
o	Ignore the AI
	Nothing happens
Worker took an off day
•	For that shift the subjob is not worked
•	Options:
o	Find a replacement
	Spawns sub decision for if this replacement worker messed it up
•	The subjob takes a couple shifts longer because of rework
	The worker needn’t fail though so often the subjob can continue normally when a replacement is used
o	Hold the job until suitable worker returns next shift

